These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, mystery
1. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is not to the right of the person watching mystery movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | horror |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: gospel, punk
1. the fan of gospel is on the far right##1
2. the fan of gospel is not to the left of the fan of punk##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | punk | gospel |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, skiing
1. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is skiing##5
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
3. the person who's sport is golf is not to the right of the person who's sport is golf##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| Sport   | golf | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-4::.
